  <h1 class="gd-h1">Heliskiing in Norway</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">Norway offers some of the most dramatic sea-to-summit skiing on earth, with steep Arctic peaks plunging straight into the fjords of the Lyngen Alps and Lofoten. This guide covers where to go, the March to May season, the terrain and how it works, before pointing you towards our <a href="/packages">packages</a> and neighbouring <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
